    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## WF-EMAIL-03 — Reply Detection\n\nReceives GHL webhook when contact replies to cold email.\nChecks if reply is positive (interested) or negative.\n\nPositive → Tag interested → Create opportunity at Walkthrough Scheduled → Telegram alert → Update data table\nNegative → Tag not interested → Update data table\n\n⚠️ SETUP:\n1. Wire GHL API credential\n2. Wire N8N API credential (for data table updates)\n3. Set up GHL webhook to POST to: https://n8n.wadeglobal.ai/webhook/email-reply-webhook\n4. Replace YOUR_GHL_LOCATION_ID_ACS\n5. Add TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN to N8N environment variables",
        "height": 300,
        "width": 500,
        "color": 4
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [180, 40],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "setup-note-003",
      "name": "Setup Instructions"
    }
